name: Carol Anne Hilton, MBA
body: Carol Anne Hilton, MBA@Hesquiaht27 Oct 2022The original economy ##yyj#indigenomicsSonghees Nation@SongheesNation26 Oct 2022Potlatch at Songhees village 1872. The roofs of the big houses are lined with blankets to be gifted, Chief Sqwameyuqs will gift a canoe to each of the visiting Chiefs. The mat-covered structure against one of the houses conceals dancers waiting to perform. Canoes line the shore.2
